OL,3,CPolice officer charged after
OL,4,Cpedestrian seriously injured in crash
OL,6,FA police officer has been charged
OL,7,Fafter a crash which left a pedestrian
OL,8,Fseriously injured.
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Police constable
OL,11,FSam Lockley, 34, was driving a marked
OL,12,Fpolice vehicle when he attempted to
OL,13,Fstop a suspected drunk driver on Drake
OL,14,FStreet, Rochdale. A pursuit followed,
OL,15,Fwhich lasted about a minute.
