OL,3,CPolice officer charged after
OL,4,Cpedestrian seriously injured in crash
OL,6,FThe police vehicle crashed into a
OL,7,Fpedestrian on the footpath of Rochdale
OL,8,FRoad on 19 November 2023, at about
OL,9,F3.30am, a spokesman for the
OL,10,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,11,F(IOPC) said.
OL,13,FFollowing the collision, Lockley was
OL,14,Fcharged with causing serious injury by
OL,15,Fdangerous driving.
OL,17,FThe spokesperson added: "The
OL,18,Fpedestrian suffered serious injuries
OL,19,Fas a result of the collision and has
OL,20,Freceived extensive medical treatment
OL,21,Fsince."
